Package PatientManagment

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    This will hold the main contents of the app
    Doctor
    This class will be assigned to a location and be able to alter diagnosis and add a perscription
    Insurance
    This class can view the payment information of the patient and the diagnosis
    Location
    Used as a model class, will hold the information of doctors, nurses etc and patients at the location
    Nurse
    This class will be assigned to a locaiton and alter patient information like heartrate, and room number
    Patient
    This class is used as a model that holds all the patient information.
    Pharm
    This class is located at a pharmacy or hospital, and can view perscriptions and edit them
    Secretary
    This class can add appointments, add patients to the system, and change the status of the patient
    User
    This is the base class for a user in the system.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    LocationType
    A list of possible locations for a user to work
    Status
    This is an enum that the nurse edits to describe where the patient is
    UserType
    this enum is used to designate the type of user being assigned
